==English==

===Noun===
'''hurling'''
#An [[Irish]] game of [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Celt Celtic] origin dating from AD400. It is played with an ash stick called a [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hurley_%28stick%29 camán] and a hard leather ball called a [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sliotar sliotar].

#A [[Cornish]] street game resembling [[rugby]], played with a silver ball.